<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="display-4 text-primary">How You Can Help with Animal Conservation</h2>
    <p class="lead">Everyday actions can make a big difference in protecting our planet's wildlife. Here are some ways you can contribute:</p>

    <ul class="list-group mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>1. Reduce, Reuse, Recycle:</strong> Minimize waste by recycling and reusing products.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>2. Support Sustainable Products:</strong> Choose sustainably made products.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>3. Volunteer for Local Conservation Projects:</strong> Get involved with local wildlife groups.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>4. Donate to Wildlife Charities:</strong> Support organizations through donations.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>5. Educate Others:</strong> Share knowledge about conservation.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>6. Avoid Single-Use Plastics:</strong> Use reusable bags, bottles, and containers.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>7. Be a Responsible Pet Owner:</strong> Ensure your pets do not harm local wildlife.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>8. Participate in Citizen Science:</strong> Join projects like bird counts and wildlife surveys.</li>
    </ul>

